---cson
layout: 'frontpage'
title: 'Mind and Reality: Nine Weeks of Philosophy'
---

include ../../fragments/outline_mixins


html: body(style='background-color:#f5f5f5')
  //- div(style="background-image:url('/img/bkg/mix/bkg02.jpg');background-position:center center; background-repeat:no-repeat; background-size:contain;width:100vw;height:100vh; position:absolute; left:0;top:0;opacity:.5;z-index:-1")
  //- img(src='/img/bkg/mix/bkg02.jpg', style='position:absolute; left:0;top:0;width:100%;height:auto;opacity:.5;z-index:-1')
  //- .mix-container(style='mix-blend-mode:overlay')

  .hero-unit
    h1 Mind and Reality
    h2 
    p --- lecturer: s.butterfill@warwick.ac.uk
    p A course at the University of Warwick.
  
  .row
    .span9
      #slides_and_handouts
        h2 Week-by-Week Guide
        p Here’s everything you need to do each week, organised by the nine weeks of the course.
          | (There is no week 6 because that is reading week.)

        p I’ll be updating things for each of the weeks until at least the Monday it starts.

      //- now do a section for each lecture
      each week in getCollection("weeks").toJSON()
        if week.hidden && getEnvironment() === 'static'
          //- pass
        else
          div(id='#{week.basename}', style='border:1px solid black; background-color:white; padding:15px;margin-bottom:1em;')
            div.titleBlock(style='background-color:#f1c9030d;margin:-15px -1000px -15px -1000px; padding:15px 1000px 15px 1000px')
              h2: a(href='/#{week.basename}.html') #{week.title}
                if week.theme
                  span : #{week.theme}
              if week.start_date
                p Commencing #{moment(week.start_date).format('dddd Do MMMM YYYY')}
            hr

            +show_week(week)

    .span3
      h4 Not what you were looking for?
      p There is also ...
      ul
        li: a(href='index-lectures.html') an outline of lectures;
        li: a(href='index-list-of-weeks.html') an index of weeks; 
        li: a(href='https://yyrama.butterfill.com/course/view/MindAndReality_2020' target='_blank') a list of seminar tasks on yyrama; and
        li: a(href='https://ex.zoxiy.xyz/course/UK_W20_Mind_and_Reality/exerciseSet/2020_21' target='_blank')  the in-lecture micro tasks on zoxiy.
      p ... or go to
      +list_weeks
